item.title: About Us
item.description: Hi there! My name is Sable and I’m so excited to tell you about our family business, Sable’s Market! My dad and I started this business together because we love fresh, delicious produce and we want to share that love with our community. At Sable’s Market, we sell all sorts of fresh fruits and vegetables! We’ve got juicy tomatoes, crispy bell peppers, sweet corn, crunchy carrots, leafy lettuce, and so much more!
